00:30:26,959 --> 00:30:29,072
Patrick, are you listening to me? 

620
00:30:29,072 --> 00:30:32,565
Come out now and we'll work something out. I promise. 

621
00:30:32,565 --> 00:30:33,420
He promised! 

622
00:30:33,420 --> 00:30:34,488
Shut up, you! 

