00:30:50,582 --> 00:30:52,063
Then do it! 

631
00:30:52,736 --> 00:30:54,154
And get it over with!

632
00:30:54,720 --> 00:30:55,193
Fine.

633
00:30:55,193 --> 00:30:56,447
Don't antagonize him, for God's sake! 

634
00:30:56,447 --> 00:30:58,420
In which case the police will be charging in to shoot you! 

635
00:30:58,420 --> 00:30:59,191
Stop it! 

