00:31:01,849 --> 00:31:04,919
There is a way out. Let me talk to them. 

637
00:31:04,919 --> 00:31:06,938
If I can get you out of this, Patrick, 

638
00:31:06,938 --> 00:31:09,369
let me try. Let me try. 

639
00:31:12,100 --> 00:31:13,115
No. 

