00:38:57,328 --> 00:39:01,020
Patrick, release Mr. Donnell and we'll send in the DA. 

760
00:39:01,020 --> 00:39:02,433
No. No way. 

761
00:39:02,433 --> 00:39:04,069
Patrick, please! 

